Golden Milk Vegan Ice Cream

3 c coconut milk
1" piece ginger, thinly sliced
1/4 c honey + more for garnish
2 tsp ground tuneric
1/2 tsp ground cinnamon
1/2 tsp kosher salt
1/4 tsp ground cardamom
1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper
1 vanilla bean, seeds scraped
chopped candied ginger for garnish

In a medium saucepan, whisk together all the ingredients minus the candied ginger, and bring to a simmer over medium heat. Let cool completely, the refrigerate overnight. Make sure you freeze the bowl of an ice cream maker during this time. The next day, strain the base into the bowl of the ice cream maker and churn per manufacturer's directions. Scrape into a shallow dish and freeze for at least 4 hrs.

